                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <locus target="#6" facs="007">Fol. 6</locus>
                    <desc>
                    orange yarn is sewn into the fore edge to mark content as navigation system;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#12" facs="013">Fol. 12</locus>
                    <desc>
                    blue yarn is sewn into the fore edge to mark content as navigation system;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
